Derivative Practice and Slope

Section 3 #A

function_1 <- expression(x ^ 2)
dx_dy <- D(function_1, 'x')
x <- 3
eval(dx_dy)
## [1] 6

#B

function_2 <- expression( 2 * (3 * a + 2) ^ 4 - 5)
da_dy <- D(function_2, 'a')
a <- 1.2
eval(da_dy)
## [1] 4214.784

#C

function_3 <- expression(((-4 * t) / (t ^ 2 + 1) ^ 3))
dt_dy <- D(function_3, 't')
t = 0
eval(dt_dy)
## [1] -4
